Results


We recruited 1484 participants from 17 centers across the XYZ Cancer Research Network between February 2002 and October 2008. Mock participants were mock randomly assigned to one of 3 treatments: A: IFL, F: FOLFOX, and G: IROX, in a 1:2:1 ratio for up to 24 weeks.


Demographics


Baseline characteristics were well balanced between the two groups (see Table 1).
